title: DDFP 300: Harvin trade & AFC playoff picture
itunes:title: DDFP 300: Harvin trade & AFC playoff picture
description:
Shek is joined by Bucky Brooks to discuss if the Seahawks can overcome the loss of Percy Harvin and the future of Jameis Winston. Daniel Jeremiah then joins the show for an early preview of the AFC playoff picture.
